{"tid":509674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前新聞小花周嘉儀騷黑絲長腿   分享聖誕喜悅","createTime":"2017-12-25T14:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:06:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":93,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"bd71601bc56ad2cc3c6d661629e21a03eac3e704","tid":509674,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:52:20.000Z","msg":"聖誕節係一個普天同慶嘅日子，好多藝人名人都會喺社交網同大家開心share佢哋點慶祝，連前新聞主播周嘉儀(Venus)都唔例外，佢今朝就喺ig度貼咗幾張聖誕開派對嘅相，重點唔係收到咩禮物或者有咩食物，而係Venus大騷佢嘅長腿呀(心心眼)！<br />\n<br />\n今朝Venus喺ig貼圖留言話：「聖誕節係普天同慶嘅日子，買禮物開party當然開心，但+2覺得最重要係分享喜悅同埋愛，無論係一個祝福一個問候定係一份小禮物，都已經係一個非常好嘅心意同祝福，就趁呢個佳節將你哋嘅愛，分享俾其他人啦，+2都祝各位有個非常愉快、充實同有意義嘅聖誕節」，最後Venus就hashtag話：「#循例都要影返幾張開party相嘅 #三個頭飾都唔同㗎 #鍾意鹿角定小紅帽」。<br />\n<br />\nVenus話三個頭飾都唔同，咁你哋又最鍾意邊款呢！？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171225/large/1514174886_cd95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171225%2Flarge%2F1514174886_cd95.jpg&h=c4ee4677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171225/large/1514174883_c852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171225%2Flarge%2F1514174883_c852.jpg&h=961869af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171225/large/1514174888_ffa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171225%2Flarge%2F1514174888_ffa7.jpg&h=c005d2ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dd7739c606f0d92060121bc7c9e6c1a28fcdc68","tid":509674,"uid":49974,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"哇屌今晚唔洗瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"